disableParam_NT.Wiki: Parameters marked with are excluded in the NT version package.

ContactLandSeId.AltName: Contact Land on Death - SE ID
ContactLandSeId.Wiki: SEID pronounced when contacting the ground after death. (-1: Invalid). SEID category is fixed to c

ContactLandAddSeId.AltName: Contact Land on Death - Additional SE ID
ContactLandAddSeId.Wiki: Additional SEID (for material) that sounds when it comes into contact with the ground after death. (-1: Invalid). SEID category is fixed to c

ContactLandPlayNum.AltName: Contact Land on Death - Play Count
ContactLandPlayNum.Wiki: Number of pronunciations when touching the ground after death

IsEnablePlayCountPerRigid.AltName: Enable Play Count per Rigid Body Unit
IsEnablePlayCountPerRigid.Wiki: Do you count the number of pronunciations of surface contact after death in rigid body units? (: Rigid body unit, : Character unit)

ContactLandMinImpuse.AltName: Contact Land on Death - Min Impulse
ContactLandMinImpuse.Wiki: Minimum impulse value required for ground contact determination after death

ContactLandMinSpeed.AltName: Contact Land on Death - Min Speed
ContactLandMinSpeed.Wiki: Minimum speed value required for ground contact determination after death

ContactPlayerSeId.AltName: Contact Player on Death - SE ID
ContactPlayerSeId.Wiki: SEID that sounds when you come into contact with Player after death. (-1: Invalid). SEID category is fixed to c

ContactPlayerMinImpuse.AltName: Contact Player on Death - Min Impulse
ContactPlayerMinImpuse.Wiki: Minimum impulse value required for Player contact judgment after death

ContactPlayerMinSpeed.AltName: Contact Player on Death - Min Speed
ContactPlayerMinSpeed.Wiki: Minimum speed value required for Player contact judgment after death
